      "source": [
        "Let's compare our rejection sampling results with the `bilby_mcmc` results. To do this, we will create a histogram of the $f$ samples for both:"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 22,
      "id": "104209a8",
      "metadata": {
